****terraform.tfstate*****

The terraform.tfstate file stores the current state of your infrastructure.
It keeps a record of all resources created by Terraform(VMs, networks, databases, etc.).
Know what already exists
When you run terraform plan or terraform apply, Terraform checks this file to know what is already created and what needs to change.
